400
00:36:05,903 --> 00:36:07,256
Parfait.

401
00:36:08,063 --> 00:36:09,052
Parlons d'argent.

402
00:36:10,743 --> 00:36:11,698
Y a un souci.

403
00:36:11,983 --> 00:36:13,052
Quel genre ?

404
00:36:13,343 --> 00:36:14,458
Ce genre-là.

405
00:36:15,143 --> 00:36:16,974
Comme ça, j'ai la paix.

406
00:36:18,463 --> 00:36:20,215
- Descends-le.
- Avec joie.

407
00:36:20,503 --> 00:36:21,413
Grosse erreur.

408
00:36:25,423 --> 00:36:27,539
